Package com.gui.hoonigan

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AccountRecoveryFrame
    AccountRecoveryFrame class This class creates a frame, that allows a user to enter their first and last name.
    AddItemFrame
    AddItemFrame This class creates a frame, which allows an Administrator to manually add an item to the library.
    AdminFrame
    AdminFrame class This class displays a frame, offering multiple admin commands, such as saving the state of the library, reading the error log, manually adding new library items, and reading a XML/JSON file to mass-load the library archives.
    CheckInFrame
    CheckInFrame class This class allows users to check in library items.
    CheckOutFrame
    CheckOutFrame class This class creates a frame, which allows the user to search the Library for items, and check the item(s) out
    DeleteUserFrame
    DeleteUserFrame class This class creates a frame that allows an Admin to delete a client.
    Driver
    HooniganGUIDriver class This class instantiates the GUI for the Hoonigan Library system.
    IdentifyYourselfFrame
    IdentifyYourselfFrame class This class creates a frame, which is meant for Username/Password recovery.
    LoadLibraryFileFrame
    LoadLibraryFileFrame This class creates the frame, where an ADMIN can load a mass Library file [in JSON/XML format].
    LoadLibraryStateFrame
    LoadLibraryStateFrame This class creates the frame, where an ADMIN can load Library state files [in JSON format].
    OpeningFrame
    OpeningFrame class This class creates a frame, which prompts the user for login information.
    RegisterNewUserFrame
    RegisterNewUserFrame class This class creates a frame that allows the User to register a new Hoonigan Account.
    SearchResultsFrame
    CheckOutFrame class This class creates a frame, which allows the user to search the Library for items, and check the item(s) out
    SecurityAnswerFrame
    SecurityAnswerFrame class This class creates a frame, which fetches the user's Security Question, and prompts them for an answer.
    SingletonInformationExpert
    SingletonInformationExpert Singleton pattern & Information Expert pattern.
    TermsAndConditionsFrame
    TermsAndConditionsFrame class This class creates a frame, which displays the Terms and Conditions of the Hoonigan Library.
    UserFrame
    UserFrame class This class creates a frame, which allows the User to either proceed to checking in an item, checking out an item, or logging out.
